Public read-only version of my personal inbox: https://public.ducksboard.com/5fNwopLHfIADlzqGQpxd/

("Later" is a Gmail label I'm tracking.)

No server required- just open a new Google Spreadsheet, apply this script, configure your settings, and set a time-based trigger. 

Google Apps Script will send the data directly to Ducksboard.

Created for the Ducksboard Hackathon, Nov 2011